      "description": "Aqualine Ltd. provides emergency repair services for water supply products to individual and corporate clients in Japan. It offers a range of services, including unclogging blocks in toilets, kitchens, washrooms, bathroom leaks, and clogs; repairing leaks; selling plumbing products, and plumbing; and renovating water supply systems, as well as customer-oriented services, such as dedicated customer",
